      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It runs but has significant mechanical issues that will require attention. The exterior shows heavy wear, including scratches, dents, and other visible damage. The interior is worn and shows signs of age and use. This vehicle is best suited for someone willing to invest in repairs or looking for a parts car.",
